Package lab5.system.model

Class SpaceMarine

java.lang.Object
lab5.system.model.SpaceMarine
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<SpaceMarine>
public class SpaceMarine extends Object implements Comparable<SpaceMarine>
Represents a SpaceMarine entity with various attributes such as id, name, coordinates, health, loyalty, achievements, melee weapon, and chapter. This class provides constructors for initializing these attributes and methods for generating hash codes, equality checks, and string representation.
